ices in terms of lower\ndimensional point configurations that they project to, with techniques that can\nbe applied to higher dimensions and larger classes of lattice polytopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Aug 2019 17:56:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2019 11:55:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 11 Apr 2020 11:24:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-05"}
